{"tid":464964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中年婦踩名貴單車被撞　的士司機出血賠兩萬","createTime":"2017-11-11T05:35:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-11T06:12:15.000Z","uid":20933,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0a831a9ee8ccc281ba1d914507a2d2877cc87f8f","tid":464964,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T05:35:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171111/large/1510348758_c307.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171111%2Flarge%2F1510348758_c307.jpg&h=5b8486d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一對中年夫婦，踩名貴單車夜遊尖沙嘴，妻子被的士撞倒，車毀人傷。凌晨約4時14分，一輛的士沿尖沙嘴山林道左轉彌敦道之際，撞倒沿彌敦道駛至的單車，47歲姓黃的單車女墮地扭傷右腳，單車尾輪變形，車架亦告損毀。<br />\n<br />\n兩夫婦踩的單車是美國名廠Cannondale，警方到場調查，姓詹的士司機(59歲)願意賠償2萬元和解了事。女傷者現場敷治後拒絕送院。"},{"pid":"b48813e34aea4ae0c3219f9cb5e2b54c49243890","tid":464964,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T05:36:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171111/large/1510348743_f6f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171111%2Flarge%2F1510348743_f6f0.jpg&h=bdb18ee1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n單車女協助警方調查，左邊戴眼鏡者為的士司機。(潘志能攝)"},{"pid":"0ef26bc0b6a3f844be2069753643ad2bdb099589","tid":464964,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T05:36:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171111/57444595\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171111%2F57444595&d=rn6nqviaFVW1ElLVK9xn%2FjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=ae92b42a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171111%2F57444595&h=ca0fce9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171111/57444595</a>"},{"pid":"